AMENDEDANALYSIS
This bill allows licensees subject to certain disciplinary matters that did not involve criminal acts,
fraud,deceit,patientsafety,publicsafety,oractsimpactingtheintegrityoftheprofession,andthatdidnot
include suspension or permanent revocation of license, to petition to have the disciplinary records
expunged.
